---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config/site';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Novalink Technologies covering data collection, usage, retention, and contact rights."
>
  <section class="container-shell pt-14">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm text-slate-600">
      Novalink Technologies handles personal data in a practical and responsible way to support enquiries, project delivery, and communication with clients and prospects.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container-shell pt-12">
    <div class="panel space-y-4 p-6 text-sm text-slate-600">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">1. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect contact details, business information, project requirements, and communication records when you contact us through WhatsApp, email, or this website.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">2. How We Use Data</h2>
      <p>We use data to respond to enquiries, scope and deliver services, provide project updates, and maintain service quality.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">3. Sharing and Processors</h2>
      <p>We only share data with service providers needed for communication, hosting, analytics, payment-related implementation support, or project operations. We do not sell personal data.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">4. Retention and Security</h2>
      <p>We keep data only as long as needed for service delivery, legal, or operational purposes and apply reasonable technical and administrative safeguards.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">5. Your Rights and Contact</h2>
      <p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data where applicable. For privacy requests, contact <a class="font-medium text-brand-800" href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}>{siteConfig.email}</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">6. Malaysia Context</h2>
      <p>This policy is intended to align with applicable Malaysian privacy and data protection requirements, including practical compliance with the Personal Data Protection Act 2010 (PDPA) where relevant.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">7. Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will always be published on this page.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
